title: Tarja - The Warm Up Concerts 2007 Show DVD
description:
Tarja - The Warm Up Concerts 2007 Show 

Live in Kuusankoski Finland - 8th of December 2007

This DVD was created from the original file made available for free download by Tarja and her record label.
The original file was cropped and resized into anamorphic widescreen, colour and gamma correction was added aswell as deblocking, noise reduction and sharpening filters.
The original audio was extracted to LPCM and left untouched to avoid further compression.
